WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:26.920 --> 00:00:30.260
Wash the chicken and set aside

00:00:30.260 --> 00:00:41.300
Fill a pot with cold water, place the chicken into the pot and cover

00:00:41.300 --> 00:00:50.180
add the the scallion segments and ginger slices, make sure the water covers the chicken

00:01:30.320 --> 00:01:42.300
bring to a boil over high heat, then turn down to low heat and cook for another 10 minutes

00:01:49.120 --> 00:01:55.100
Remove bubbles and impurities as they rise to the surface

00:02:00.660 --> 00:02:11.700
Turn off the heat, cover the pan and leave it for 30 minutes.

00:02:24.540 --> 00:02:41.200
Take out the cooked chicken,

00:03:36.940 --> 00:03:45.420
drench with rice wine and rub all-over with salt

00:04:17.460 --> 00:04:22.560
Set aside to cool then cut the chicken up into pieces.

